subject: Basketball (College)
Diamond Head Classic (College Basketball)
lead_paragraph: Kethan Savage scored 12 points and led a late rally as George Washington beat No. 11 Wichita State, 60-54, on Thursday in the final of the Diamond Head Classic in Honolulu.
